# ===== Reusable JUCE / Projucer .gitignore =====
# Commit SOURCE only (.jucer + Source/). Everything below is generated
# by Projucer/Xcode and can be regenerated, so we don't track it.

# Projucer-generated IDE projects (Xcode, Visual Studio, etc.)
Builds/

# Projucer-generated JUCE module wrappers
JuceLibraryCode/

# Xcode per-user state (window layout, breakpoints) — not shareable
*.xcuserdatad
xcuserdata/

# macOS Finder metadata junk
.DS_Store
